transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello, haanji sir bataiye.
Customer: Haanji haanji wo kya theek hai yaar aapko nahi samajh mein kuch lag rahi.
Executive: Kya sir?
Customer: Aapko na samajh mein lag rahi kuch aapka dimaag ya use nahi karna chahte ya hai nahi.
Executive: Dono cheez mein abhi maine haan haan abhi maine aapko lead send kiya tha. Abhi dekho saat minute pehle saat minute pehle sold out hai. Batao mujhe isme kya hai?
Customer: Saat minute apni baat karte karte sold out ho jayegi.
Executive: Apni baat saat minute pehle kar lo.
Customer: Achcha ye ACS subscriber seat ki jo buying ki daal rakhi hai do hour ago. Theek hai? Shopler Rajasthan. Main mere meri ye baat ka jawab nahi de rahe aap.
Executive: Haan bataiye.
